version_description: There is no capo on this version of the song, or alternative tunings, to make it easier. The strumming pattern mentioned is just a guideline, so feel free to mix up your strumming as much as you want. If you listen to the song, it will probably make it easier to figure out.
Transcribed from the official lyrics video on Train's YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lv_kecbON_g.
